## Limitations

The report is based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on the topic. Some sources may have publication dates beyond the current data training cut-off, and the information may not reflect the most recent developments in the field. Additionally, the focus was primarily on U.S.-based resources, which may limit the applicability of findings to other regions.